milestones.description: Dennis Lillee has become the top wicket-taker for AUS in ODIs with 18 wickets, going past Max Walker's 17
Doug Walters has broken the record for most catches (7) in ODIs for AUS, going past Greg Chappell's 6
Rod Marsh has broken the record for most dismissals (29) in ODIs, going past Deryck Murray's 28
